.contents
Smoke'em Poker		Multi-player draw-poker game. Try to relieve five
		computer players of their money. Easy-to-use graphic
		interface, configurable preferences, multi-tasking and
		system-friendly. Version 1.4.1 adds stats graphing, key
		shortcuts, sound effects, bug fixes, and more prefs.
		Requires WB 2.x or later, 2 megs of memory, WB overscan
		speech requires Amiga speech software, no external
		libraries required.  Version 1.4.1, binary only, freeware.
		Author:  Dave O'Brien
